Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO LOCAL GOVERNMENT

Title: Authorizes the town of Brookhaven, county of Suffolk, to alienate certain lands used as parkland and to dedicate certain other lands as parklands
Summary: Authorizes the town of Brookhaven, county of Suffolk, to alienate certain lands used as parkland and to dedicate certain other lands as parklands.
ActClause: AN ACT to authorize the town of Brookhaven, county of Suffolk, to alienate and discontinue the use of certain parklands
